A Cluster is the entire OpenShift or Kubernetes environment â€” all nodes, networking, storage, API servers, and workloads working together under one control plane.
ğŸ‘‰ It is the topmost unit in OpenShift â€” it contains everything (projects, namespaces, pods, etc.).

